<inglise> Whereas it is necessary to ensure that when this Directive is applied cooperation between Member States and the Commission will be as effective as possible; whereas the detailed rules for the application of the Directive must be adopted after an opinion has been given by the Standing Committee for Agricultural Statistics set up by Decision 72/279/EEC (2); </inglise>
<eesti> on vaja tagada, et kui kohaldatakse k&auml;esolevat direktiivi, peab liikmesriikide ja komisjoni vaheline koost&ouml;&ouml; olema nii t&otilde;hus kui v&otilde;imalik; k&auml;esoleva direktiivi kohaldamise &uuml;ksikasjalikud eeskirjad tuleb vastu v&otilde;tta p&auml;rast 72/279/EM&Uuml; (2) otsusega loodud alalise p&otilde;llumajandusstatistika komitee arvamuse esitamist; </eesti>
