<inglise> Whereas the financial responsibility of the Community should be defined with regard to expenditure incurred by the Member States for the first survey provided for by this Directive, </inglise>
<eesti> seet&otilde;ttu tuleks m&auml;&auml;ratleda &uuml;henduse finantsvastutus kulude suhtes, mida liikmesriigid kannavad seoses esimese k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;ruse alusel tehtava vaatlusega; </eesti>
