<inglise> A. Variety of fruit </inglise>
<eesti> A. Puuviljasordid </eesti>
<inglise> For each species of fruit, and in order of importance, enough varieties must be shown to enable a separate assessment to be made for each Member State, by variety, of at least 80 % of the total area planted with fruit trees of the species in question and, in any case, all varieties representing 3 % or more of the total area planted with fruit trees of the species in question. </inglise>
<eesti> Selleks, et oleks v&otilde;imalik viljeldavate sortide j&auml;rgi liikmesriike eraldi hinnata, tuleb iga liigi puhul esitada andmed v&auml;hemalt 80 protsendil selle liigi istandike pindalast kasvatatavate sortide kohta t&auml;htsuse j&auml;rjekorras, kusjuures kindlasti esitatakse andmed iga sordi kohta, mis v&otilde;tab enda alla 3% v&otilde;i rohkem k&otilde;nesoleva viljapuuliigi istandike kogupindalast. </eesti>
