<inglise> 2. </inglise>
<eesti> 2. </eesti>
<inglise> If the Member States, in respect of the areas planted with fruit trees referred to in Article 1 (1), take note of additional characteristics complying with the purpose of this Directive, bearing for example on stock, the shapes of trees and the height of the trunk, the results must also be notified to the Commission, in so far as they are reliable. </inglise>
