<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> Member States shall notify the Commission of the results of the surveys drawn up in the prescribed form as rapidly as possible, and in any case before 1 April of the year following that in which the survey was carried out. </inglise>
